2. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) - The paper focuses on a relay network with conferencing links, which is a key aspect of networking and internet architecture. 
3. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper analyzes the performance of two relaying schemes in a network, which can be viewed as a control problem. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper may be relevant to multimedia applications that require efficient relay networks. 
5. cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science) - The paper involves mathematical analysis of the achievable rates of relaying schemes, which can be considered as a computational engineering problem.
